{"tid":2118424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆血汗口罩廠，勞役維吾爾族人兼洗腦，逼講普通話睇升旗，產品售全球！","createTime":"2020-07-21T12:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T15:52:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b05234ef0008ad167e4357105ce723b062b07a","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200721/D6ULDV7HFZYDX553GI2L566EBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200721%2FD6ULDV7HFZYDX553GI2L566EBI%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=dddfcd34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200721%2FD6ULDV7HFZYDX553GI2L566EBI%2F&h=bd468920\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200721/D6ULDV7HFZYDX553GI2L566EBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國管治新疆受到多方批評，早前美國《紐約時報》已揭發不少西方著名品牌與中國合作生產，中國向外隱瞞強迫新疆維吾爾族人作苦工。近日《紐時》再度發現，中國自疫情開始，便再次利用新疆維人，強迫他們從事生產口罩，賣到世界各地圖利。國際專家痛斥中國強迫勞動有違人權，惟中國駐美大使館回應稱：「該計劃協助當地居民過上有意義的生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pc0t2I6g3O7edw-9b0doUSmk0hg=/802x533/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6ILPFFKA7M4XHK2GMIS6H3FHNU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpc0t2I6g3O7edw-9b0doUSmk0hg%3D%2F802x533%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6ILPFFKA7M4XHK2GMIS6H3FHNU.gif&h=e4172483&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n報道引用中國國家藥品監督管理局數據，在武漢肺炎出現之前，新疆只有四間公司生產醫療級防護設備，但直至6月30日已多達51間，當中最少17間參與所謂「勞動力轉移計劃」，即是強逼新疆維人從事生產口罩。"},{"pid":"a69bf3ffee3229db18f365599c5632fbe5570e7e","tid":2118424,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"香港既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cadc2fa1700f979ded1355ccc6e5df13cffab77","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:38:52.000Z","msg":"根據中國官媒今年3月底的報道，其中一個維人工作點是烏魯木齊高新區，稱「接受首批60名南疆富餘勞動力安置就業」，形容是「奪取疫情防控和經濟社會發展雙勝利」。報道亦透露今年當地高新區會接收1,000名南疆人。「這些強制性配額會導致人們被送到不想去的工廠工作，」戰略與國際研究中心人權行動主任萊爾（Amy K. Lehr）說。「根據國際法，這可以被視為強迫勞動。」"},{"pid":"c311661b0974431ebd1531ac79617a6bc38e7600","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"《紐時》亦追蹤了湖北一間名為「湖北海興衞生用品有限公司」，該公司同樣是生產醫療設備，產品由湖北運到上海，之後再送往美國洛杉磯。報道發現該湖北工廠更強令100多名維吾爾族人到當地生產。維人在工廠必須學習普通話，教材名為「在鄂新疆籍少數民族群眾國家通用語言文字學習手冊」。中國教育部旗下《中國民族教育》雜誌曾撰文，列明該項目是要「增强文化認同、促進國家統一、維護邊疆民族地區長治久安的治本之策」，甚有政治維穩意思。"},{"pid":"eab686ac03647000dd3b817a0c75cb60dad82bc8","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"《紐時》亦發現了一間在江西德安縣的「江西美寶利醫用敷料有限公司」（Medwell），工廠勞動人口中最少25%是維人，中國官媒相片亦見「新疆職人之家」及大量維人，員工指一星期內三天要學普通話，黑板上更寫有「我們熱愛祖國」等教育字句，每星期維人亦要參加升旗儀式，保證對中國的忠誠。據中國官媒，該公司收到2,000萬個口罩定單，目前已發貨了70萬個口罩，主要送向意大利、西班牙及葡萄牙。不過，該公司回覆《紐時》，否認公司有聘請過維人。而訂貨的海外公司亦大多回覆根本不知道貨源由維人生產。"},{"pid":"de57eda8eac5ccaa587a1128ab17f38f06ebc840","tid":2118424,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"零成本，因為唔洗出糧"},{"pid":"192fe7afc124125076fdd21497b43ee92afb9021","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de57eda8eac5ccaa587a1128ab17f38f06ebc840","tid":2118424,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"零成本，因為唔洗出糧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mBPwWVvOGVCSXEXzghGe4IIwi7w=/694x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUXMORL57DSO3NB2FFHKKT4UVQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmBPwWVvOGVCSXEXzghGe4IIwi7w%3D%2F694x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRUXMORL57DSO3NB2FFHKKT4UVQ.gif&h=75bdffdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">被勞役的維吾爾族人在其中一間工廠排隊領飯。</span></p>"},{"pid":"af418d678f26a48ef4ab36462537f75088bb48c5","tid":2118424,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"當新疆人狗咁養<br />\n絕育逼佢地做野"},{"pid":"e9e655cda4fdd369079cef0997c5ae82e18c2681","tid":2118424,"uid":34804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192fe7afc124125076fdd21497b43ee92afb9021","tid":2118424,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de57eda8eac5ccaa587a1128ab17f38f06ebc840","tid":2118424,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"零成本，因為唔洗出糧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mBPwWVvOGVCSXEXzghGe4IIwi7w=/694x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUXMORL57DSO3NB2FFHKKT4UVQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmBPwWVvOGVCSXEXzghGe4IIwi7w%3D%2F694x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRUXMORL57DSO3NB2FFHKKT4UVQ.gif&h=75bdffdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">被勞役的維吾爾族人在其中一間工廠排隊領飯。</span></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"左膠：有飯食有地方住，仲有公安24小時保護，唔算侵犯人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834930d4597d8511d9166a98958ea5d40a5be241","tid":2118424,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/110000488_297533881595816_7691752606251103127_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=6h8RB3q2h_MAX94FRzH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=d371f019ebc12c8ad48d28a47503d9f4&amp;oe=5F3C24C7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F110000488_297533881595816_7691752606251103127_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D6h8RB3q2h_MAX94FRzH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dd371f019ebc12c8ad48d28a47503d9f4%26oe%3D5F3C24C7&h=e71cece0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7526d663f26cc7e877f05afc7963872e974a65e","tid":2118424,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0166f7e5de8b134a646bb1fe9021394a267a129","tid":2118424,"uid":71210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"Anti humanity"},{"pid":"46933233e7c5e2556ff848739b536048d5863abd","tid":2118424,"uid":156064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}